title: UFYB 202: Self-Worth, Dating, Rejection & Love: A Conversation with Clara Artschwager
itunes:title: Self-Worth, Dating, Rejection & Love: A Conversation with Clara Artschwager
description:
Do you analyze text messages from romantic interests like you’re peering into into a crystal ball, constantly scanning for evidence of their interest (or lack thereof)? Do you feel like your future happiness is completely at the mercy of the dating apps? In this episode, conscious dating and relationship coach Clara Artschwager and I dig into common dating anxieties and teach you how to let go of dating anxiety for good.

 

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfuckyourbrain.com/202
